ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to ensure that asylum claims are decided quickly, and to create an expedited process for claims made by claimants from a designated country of origin (DCO) relative to other claims.
